::KitKat::

She sniffed the air just inside the cave.  She could smell Rowdy.
"Rowdy, are you in here?"  She walked into the cave.  She looked and 
saw the pond.  She growled and bared her teeth at it.  She had her 
ears flat back and her tail was pointed down.
She transformed into bot mode and opened her comlink. 
"Rowdy, do you copy? it's me, KitKat. Please respond."
She was getting the same feeling now that she had when she entered 
here looking for Quickstrick. "Blast it all, Rowdy come in."
